txt.en: 'If you are truly worthy of being named a flet-runner, you will be able to make your way to the flet-runner outside the House of Celeborn in any time I name, will you not, [placeholder]?\n\n'For what are you waiting? Begin!'
'I am beside myself with surprise, [placeholder], that you have made it here in time...but you have done so!'
'Why do you delay? I will give you no additional time to find the flet-runner outside the House of Celeborn!'
